{"id": "elixir_rs-puf", "title": "Implement observlib_ex: Feature-complete Elixir reimplementation", "description": "# Implementation Plan for observlib_ex\n\nComplete Elixir reimplementation of the Python observlib library with OpenTelemetry integration.\n\n## Overview\nReimplementation using idiomatic Elixir patterns: OTP applications, supervision trees, Telemetry integration, and compile-time macros.\n\n## Reference Documentation\n- Python Analysis: ../observlib/observlib/CLAUDE.md\n- Architecture Design: ../.omc/observlib-ex-architecture.md\n- Implementation Plan: ../.omc/observlib-ex-implementation-plan.md\n\n## Implementation Phases\n\n### Phase 1: Core Infrastructure (4h - LOW)\n- [ ] ObservLib main module with public API\n- [ ] ObservLib.Application - OTP application\n- [ ] ObservLib.Config - Configuration GenServer\n- Files: lib/observlib.ex, lib/observlib/application.ex, lib/observlib/config.ex\n- Tests: test/observlib_test.exs, test/observlib/config_test.exs\n\n### Phase 2: Telemetry Foundation (2h - LOW)\n- [ ] ObservLib.Telemetry - Event handler attachment\n- File: lib/observlib/telemetry.ex\n- Test: test/observlib/telemetry_test.exs\n\n### Phase 3: Traces Module (8h - MEDIUM)\n- [ ] ObservLib.Traces.Supervisor - Supervision tree\n- [ ] ObservLib.Traces.Provider - Span management GenServer\n- [ ] ObservLib.Traces.OTLPExporter - OTLP HTTP exporter\n- [ ] ObservLib.Traces.PyroscopeProcessor - Pyroscope integration\n- Files: lib/observlib/traces/*.ex\n- Tests: test/observlib/traces/*_test.exs\n\n### Phase 4: Metrics Module (10h - MEDIUM-HIGH)\n- [ ] ObservLib.Metrics.Supervisor - Supervision tree\n- [ ] ObservLib.Metrics.MeterProvider - Metric collection GenServer\n- [ ] ObservLib.Metrics.PrometheusReader - Prometheus scrape endpoint\n- [ ] ObservLib.Metrics.OTLPExporter - OTLP HTTP exporter\n- Files: lib/observlib/metrics/*.ex\n- Tests: test/observlib/metrics/*_test.exs\n\n### Phase 5: Logs Module (6h - MEDIUM)\n- [ ] ObservLib.Logs.Supervisor - Supervision tree\n- [ ] ObservLib.Logs.Backend - Logger backend (:gen_event)\n- [ ] ObservLib.Logs.OTLPExporter - OTLP HTTP exporter\n- Files: lib/observlib/logs/*.ex\n- Tests: test/observlib/logs/*_test.exs\n\n### Phase 6: Traced Macro (12h - HIGH)\n- [ ] ObservLib.Traced - Macro for function decoration\n- File: lib/observlib/traced.ex\n- Test: test/observlib/traced_test.exs\n- Note: Complex macro metaprogramming + AST manipulation\n\n### Phase 7: Pyroscope Integration (4h - MEDIUM)\n- [ ] ObservLib.Pyroscope.Client - Pyroscope HTTP client\n- File: lib/observlib/pyroscope/client.ex\n- Test: test/observlib/pyroscope/client_test.exs\n\n### Phase 8: Integration & End-to-End Tests (6h - MEDIUM)\n- [ ] Full telemetry pipeline tests\n- [ ] OTLP export to mock server\n- [ ] Prometheus scraping tests\n- Files: test/integration/*.exs\n\n### Phase 9: Documentation & Examples (4h - LOW)\n- [ ] README.md usage guide\n- [ ] Getting started guide\n- [ ] Configuration guide\n- [ ] Custom instrumentation guide\n- [ ] Example scripts\n- Files: guides/*.md, examples/*.exs\n\n## Dependencies\n\n### Runtime\n- opentelemetry_api (~> 1.2)\n- opentelemetry (~> 1.3)\n- opentelemetry_exporter (~> 1.6)\n- opentelemetry_telemetry (~> 1.0)\n- telemetry (~> 1.2)\n- telemetry_metrics (~> 0.6)\n- telemetry_poller (~> 1.0)\n- jason (~> 1.4)\n- req (~> 0.4)\n\n### Dev/Test\n- ex_doc (~> 0.30)\n- dialyxir (~> 1.4)\n- credo (~> 1.7)\n- stream_data (~> 0.6)\n\n## Success Criteria\n- [ ] All Python observlib features implemented\n- [ ] OTLP export working (traces, metrics, logs)\n- [ ] Prometheus metrics endpoint functional\n- [ ] Pyroscope profiling integration working\n- [ ] Test coverage >90%\n- [ ] All Dialyzer warnings resolved\n- [ ] Credo checks pass\n- [ ] Documentation complete\n- [ ] Examples run successfully\n\n## Total Estimate\n~57 hours across 9 phases\n\n## Notes\n- Phase 0 (Project Setup) already complete\n- Project already initialized in observlib_ex/\n- Follow idiomatic Elixir patterns throughout\n- Use supervision trees for fault tolerance\n- Leverage Telemetry for events", "status": "open", "priority": 2, "issue_type": "task", "created_at": "2026-03-27T09:33:08.854384534Z", "created_by": "urist", "updated_at": "2026-03-27T09:33:08.854384534Z", "source_repo": ".", "compaction_level": 0, "original_size": 0, "labels": ["epic", "planning"]}
